1. How to run

First start the server with server.sh script

Usage:  server.sh $1
Where $1 is the req_code

The server will print out the n_port it listens on
Run the client with client.sh script

Usage: client.sh $1 $2 $3 "$4"
Where $1 is server address, $2 is n_port, $3 is req_code (printed out by server), and $4 is string


2. Undergrad Machine
Ran and tested on machine ubuntu1604-004 and ubuntu1604-002 for cross machine connection


3. Using python3 interpreter
